{"tid":1739703,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣不如嘗試用利益出發去說服人?","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T17:49:24.000Z","uid":63670,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ccf2623708016b18b983626cff130e6207ab55","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:24:46.000Z","msg":"打悲情牌有用<br />\n但係要出既出曬了<br />\n不如試下用利益去引誘?<br />\n只要成功用一個禮拜大三罷<br />\n就可以換黎一張選票<br />\n你睇下選舉就到d議員幾親民?<br />\n對你地幾好？點解？因為你手上有選票<br />\n再睇下唔係香港選出黎既特首幾令人不爽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣唔擅長<br />\n但係希望刺激下大家思維<br />\n我都打算落手落腳做一份試試<br />\n利益說服永遠係最有用....不如試試<br />\n就算唔係一個即刻俾到既利益<br />\n可以嘗試俾個希望人<br />\n見得到既(如上)<br />\n<br />\n同毛澤東一樣<br />\n俾個希望農民&mdash;&mdash;-發達富貴<br />\n再將發達富貴既通道講成跟隨自己<br />\nd人就會跟隨<br />\n<br />\n即=俾個目標，俾個達到目標既手段，<br />\n就可以收穫一班人幫手<br />\nsor for 1999<br />\n但係推一推,各位都可以表達下自己認為可行既文宣方向"},{"pid":"22e8e12fdb69f560bd4908f6cae99a4f824abe4f","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"00a82c1d6e9e00239f3b342d9ab59eccd2daca4c","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17a27e589d38ea3a699ac1ae0476108de77d2f91","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"550f41d5b2e7e30d77ab2a9fd61390125b5c99c6","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:21:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fcfedc0b9f94faa81f9bf88a01bd05de4d1b7c2e","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90939c7533bf49f78625627f3cf7f3c65490d686","tid":1739703,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:29:30.000Z","msg":"訓醒一推"},{"pid":"817e1824f47b4f845b2da5b446551df311aa7eea","t